data.description: Take a step back in time to this charming, picturesque cirque 1920's cottage home. The shiplap and original wood floors along with the antique original lighting fixtures are just a few unique an invaluable factor that bring light to this beautiful home. A large 2 bed, 2 bath that was remodeled after the 2020 Hurricanes, but contractor salvaged the historic integrity.
